imdb.title: Prístav
plot: Marek Skála ('Martin Dejdar' (qv)) left his wife and floats in houseboat to the Bay Area. Here, together with his friend Roman Mares ('Filip Blazek' (qv)), he rents a pub aptly named The Port.::Czechfan
